Comment: 50,0:23:52.99,0:23:53.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 50,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So hot today...
Dialogue: 50,0:00:27.97,0:00:31.43,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,It's once again time for {\i1}Happiness Music!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:31.43,0:00:35.01,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,We hope you enjoy the performance\Nwe have lined up tonight!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, there's a music show on!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:11.03,0:02:17.37,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,Tonight's guest is the songstress\Nfrom the Moon, MashuLulu-san!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.20,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.16,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Let's see here.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:21.66,0:02:26.21,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,Lulu-san, I hear you've just made your debut\Nand this will be your first performance!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.17,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 50,0:02:28.17,0:02:32.55,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yes. B-But I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.76,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Who is that? She's so cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.97,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,Now, let's hear her perform!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.93,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,"Little singing bird"!{non-title case via ending credits}
Dialogue: 51,0:02:53.32,0:02:59.74,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ah, the dazzling light you gazed to from your window{ああ窓から見つめてた眩しさは}
Dialogue: 51,0:02:59.74,0:03:07.08,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}No matter how far you stretch, you can reach it no more{腕を伸ばしても今はもう届かない}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:07.42,0:03:14.05,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ah, like a little bird hiding in the shade{ああ日の影に隠れてる小鳥のよう}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:14.47,0:03:21.43,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You feign that you don't see your own desires{憧れも見ないふりしていた}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:21.43,0:03:28.35,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You wanted to speak, but you couldn't, so you closed yourself off{伝えたくてできなくて心閉ざしていた}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:28.77,0:03:36.07,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Even having a dream seemed to frighten you{夢見ることもどこか怯えてたの}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:36.07,0:03:44.20,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Baby, don't cry-ry-ry-ry for me, little blue bird{Baby don’t cry-ry-ry-ry for me 青いLittle Bird}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:44.20,0:03:50.63,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The wounds on your wings should heal with time{翼で傷は時が癒したはずよ}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:50.63,0:03:58.09,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Baby, fly up, fly up, fly up, into the great blue sky{Baby Fly up Fly up Fly up Blue sky(大きな空)}
Dialogue: 51,0:03:58.09,0:04:03.47,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The miracle will keep shining up ahead{その先で光る奇跡から}
Dialogue: 51,0:04:03.47,0:04:08.06,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So don't stop chasing it until you smile{追いかけ続けほほ笑むまで}
Dialogue: 51,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.56,INS,MashuLulu,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Little singing bird
