Dialogue: 50,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.99,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.62,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,No, thank you, Lulu-san,\Nfor your lovely song!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.29,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:24.29,0:04:28.25,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,No way, Shota. She's a newbie?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:28.25,0:04:28.83,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 50,0:04:29.21,0:04:31.71,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,She's so good...
Dialogue: 50,0:04:31.71,0:04:34.17,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Lulu-chan's awesome!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.93,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,I see she transformed as well.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:41.64,0:04:42.72,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,It's melting.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:46.35,0:04:50.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Uguisu, wasn't she amazing?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.65,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,She's such a good singer!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.02,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Your ice cream's melting!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Forget about the ice cream.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.40,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,She almost sounded like big sis.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I think the world's gonna love her!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.20,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Cut! That's a wrap!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.63,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,Great work, Lulu-san.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.25,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.75,Default,Kento,0,0,0,,See you again!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.84,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Good job, Lulu!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:20.84,0:05:25.97,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Toko-san! How did I do?\NI got through the song.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.68,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Don't worry, that was perfect!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:28.68,0:05:29.81,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:29.81,0:05:30.85,Default,Producer,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:30.85,0:05:35.40,Default,Producer,0,0,0,,Why, I've fallen in love with your singing!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.69,Default,Producer,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you again.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.61,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.53,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I'm sure the public loved it too!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.24,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You're about to get even busier!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.45,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Good work tonight, Lulu!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.04,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I really sang!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.94,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,This is the place...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.12,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:31.04,0:06:34.12,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,You want to join our agency? Why?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.88,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,It's so small too, who'd want to come here?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.63,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,That day, I...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:42.01,0:06:46.05,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I happened to catch the livestream\Nof Lilly's concert, and...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.51,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, the one in Shibuya?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.22,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.48,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Lilly looked like she had fun singing there.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.98,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,and I wanted to become just like her.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.99,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Then, how about you sing a little for us?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.16,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.25,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,You're good!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.08,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.79,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.55,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Sounds pretty clear-cut, right, Toko?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.30,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You really want to join us?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.43,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yes, if you'll have me.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.64,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I'd be glad to!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.18,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.81,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,By the way, what's your name?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.73,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.69,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.23,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.32,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Lu... Lu...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:42.32,0:07:46.03,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lulu? That's a cute name!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.49,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But for your stage name...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.87,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It should have something more like Lilly's.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.50,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lilly's is Compato...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.63,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Let's go with MashuLulu.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.75,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.25,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.01,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Great, your name's settled.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.47,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,So, what next, Toko?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.76,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm gonna get you on the road!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.35,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.60,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,But I can only do this for one year...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.06,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.93,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want you to perform on TV!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.06,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's just ridiculous.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go talk to the station!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.90,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.90,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,At least put on something nicer first!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.07,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,They're gone...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.49,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:30.82,0:08:35.41,Default,Staff A,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we can't, miss.\NThe program's already planned out.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.16,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Could you please find a way?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.04,Default,Staff A,0,0,0,,It's not that easy...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.00,Default,Staff B,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.38,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You'll get it once you've heard her sing!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.63,Default,Producer,0,0,0,,This just isn't a show where newcomers\Nmake their big break.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:49.63,0:08:54.18,Default,Producer,0,0,0,,It'd be different if you had Lilly come on.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.06,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That'll do! Let me make you a proposal!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.40,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I talked it over with them.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.61,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,How'd you convince them?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:03.61,0:09:08.03,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,By promising that Lilly can perform\Non their show next time.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.28,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lulu, go out and sing!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.28,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.16,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,We're going live!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.79,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'm going on!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.08,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.93,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Rui, you did great today.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:35.76,0:09:39.85,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I actually became an idol...
Dialogue: 50,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.90,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,You did! And you were wonderful!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.94,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I'm your fan too!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.44,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Thank you, Azuki.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.78,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.32,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Rui.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:52.91,0:09:56.24,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You're pretty late. Did something happen?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:56.24,0:10:00.20,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing serious. Sorry.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey, Uguisu.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:05.84,0:10:09.76,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Does something seem off about big sis?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:09.76,0:10:10.71,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just imagining it.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.81,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I did it! I was brave!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.23,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.19,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Fuu-chan, did you catch {\i1}Happiness Music{\i0} last night?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.19,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I did. It was Lulu-chan, right?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.74,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,She was amazing!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.86,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,And she's such a great singer!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.83,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah! Not to mention, she was so cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:37.83,0:10:38.53,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, Sho-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.21,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey, last night on TV...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.42,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Oh, is this about Lulu?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.38,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,She's even big with the middle schoolers...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.80,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone{\i0} saw it.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:51.34,0:10:55.80,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So, Sho-chan, which one do you like better?\NLilly or Lulu?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.80,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Huh? Hmm, which one...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.68,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Lilly... Lulu... I can't pick.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.81,Default,Fuu / Iroha,0,0,0,,{\an8}So? So? Which one is it?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.19,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:05.19,0:11:08.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.77,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.57,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:11.57,0:11:12.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.37,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I finished a new confection today,
Dialogue: 50,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.87,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,and wanted my friend to sample it,
Dialogue: 50,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.17,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,but I can't bring them now.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.63,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Your friend? Who is it?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:29.63,0:11:33.05,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mari-chan. She's visited from time to time.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.17,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Should I deliver them?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.43,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,No, it's too far for you.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:37.43,0:11:40.43,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It'll be fine! I'm a fifth grader now!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.43,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.52,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have you do it, then.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.15,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.90,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Message me when you get there.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.73,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Will do! See you later!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:56.32,0:11:59.41,Default,Train Annc.,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next stop, Yoyogi. Yoyogi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.58,Default,Train Annc.,0,0,0,,{\i1}The doors will open on the left side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.04,Default,Train Annc.,0,0,0,,{\i1}Transfer to the Toei Subway Koedo Line...{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.79,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:06.79,0:12:07.58,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.29,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:15.42,0:12:19.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's the place right next to the agency!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.76,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.43,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.43,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.69,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,My, Fuu!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.69,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,You've grown so much!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Mari-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.94,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,Any problems getting here?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.69,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,This is from Mom!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.74,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:37.74,0:12:41.07,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,I was thinking of selling some of\Nyour shop's confections here too.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.57,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,Take a seat.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.54,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,I'll get you some ice-cold juice\Nas a show of thanks.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Thank... you...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.50,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,Here. Thank you for coming all this way.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.42,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:08.89,0:13:12.31,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I have to text Mom.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.15,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,"I made it."
Dialogue: 50,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,"She gave me some juice."
Dialogue: 50,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Toko-san.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:23.37,0:13:26.33,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lilly, where are you at?{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.71,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,"I'm at the café by the agency."
Dialogue: 50,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect timing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:32.21,0:13:37.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's someone I want to introduce to you.\NGuess who it is... You'll be surprised!{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.93,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,"Wanna come over?"
Dialogue: 50,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.80,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'll be surprised?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Shank yew!{speaking with food in mouth}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.02,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:57.36,0:14:01.53,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I'll reach out to you\Nwhen your schedule is set.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:02.45,0:14:07.28,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lulu, looks like your idol's\Nat the café next door!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.33,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Really? I'll go see her!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.46,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,W-Wait! She said she's coming here!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.17,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,She took off.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:23.97,0:14:27.26,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot! I have to transform!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.14,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Really, here?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:32.94,0:14:33.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Litto!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Pam pam power!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it really be...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 50,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.73,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.99,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Where's the person you told me about?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:23.99,0:15:27.53,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lulu wanted to see you so badly,\Nshe went off to Dubdub.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.70,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lulu-chan! I knew it was her!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.33,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'll go after her!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.83,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Come on...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.33,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Both of you are so impatient.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.09,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What are you, children?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.80,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,It looks like she left already.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.60,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the agency.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.73,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:00.73,0:16:05.36,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I wonder what I should say to Lilly.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.36,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Lulu?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:07.86,0:16:11.16,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'll cast a spell to ease my nerves.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.87,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Lululila pululila,
Dialogue: 50,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.58,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,make me calm down.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.84,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,That's silly.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.13,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:31.43,0:16:34.77,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Maybe walking up slowly\Nis supposed to calm me down?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.39,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.14,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wh... What...
Dialogue: 50,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.90,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,The staircase got super long!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Did my magic do this?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.61,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Let's just go down.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.00,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I can't see the bottom at all...
Dialogue: 50,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.33,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Now we might never see Lulu-chan.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.89,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,This song...
Dialogue: 50,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.31,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of person Lilly is.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.61,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,D-Do you think we'll get along?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.11,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I think you will.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.37,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I hope we'll get to sing together someday!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:34.87,0:17:35.62,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lulu-chan! If you're there, say something back!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.71,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.88,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Is that you, Lilly-san?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.38,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I saw you on TV!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.39,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I loved your song!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:55.39,0:18:00.77,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Um, I saw your livestream too!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Really? I'm glad!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.77,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,It made me start to chase my dream!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:07.23,0:18:11.95,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I was afraid to sing,\Nbut when I heard you do it...
Dialogue: 50,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.70,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I realized I wanted to try it too!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.58,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:18.37,0:18:22.00,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So, Lulu-chan! Do you like animals?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.38,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:25.38,0:18:29.50,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Like what? My favorite are hippos!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.67,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,You're gonna get caught!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:31.05,0:18:33.43,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Hippos? Interesting...
Dialogue: 50,0:18:33.80,0:18:37.05,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,My favorite are cats!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.85,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Aw, I want to see you so bad,\Nbut I can't reach you at all.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.31,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I have to stop the spell.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.90,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Tohre!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lulu-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 50,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.04,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Lulu-chan?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:03.29,0:19:05.62,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,We were so close...
Dialogue: 50,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.59,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hello, Toko-san?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:09.59,0:19:12.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.09,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You're gonna keep missing each other.\NJust wait at the café!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.30,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.52,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,My transformation wore off.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.48,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:25.48,0:19:29.11,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Come on. What were you doing?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.44,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.11,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Alright, meet our newest member!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.82,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,There you are! Finally!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.53,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Um, I'm Lulu!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.20,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I-It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm Lilly! Nice to meet you too!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.66,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:45.66,0:19:49.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lulu-chan, you're so stiff.\NYou weren't like that before.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.92,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I-I get nervous talking face-to-face.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.51,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Oh, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:57.51,0:20:01.51,Default,Mari,0,0,0,,Toko-chan, glad to see\Nyou've gotten more members.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.47,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's great!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:03.47,0:20:07.19,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You've been watching over us\Nsince we started, right?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:07.19,0:20:10.65,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Now we have two big new stars\Nand things are getting crazy!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.32,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,The agency's really starting to grow.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:14.40,0:20:18.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,The way we kept missing each other,\NI thought we'd never meet!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.95,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was rough.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wasn't that staircase weird too?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.95,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wait, Azuki?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.41,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I-It sure was...
Dialogue: 50,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.04,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Sorry, I gotta go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.92,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Huh? O-Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.17,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Uguisu?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.18,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,I came with!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.39,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Azuki, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.18,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I tagged along!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.56,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You did? That's surprising.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:46.43,0:20:50.69,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Now, a toast to Lilly and Lulu's debut!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:50.69,0:20:54.02,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Let's all work our hardest together!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.15,Default,Everyone,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.40,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I guess milk is kinda childish, isn't it?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.49,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.74,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That's a lot of sugar, Lulu...
Dialogue: 50,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.20,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,So you have a sweet tooth.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.29,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.33,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Hopefully we fooled them.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.25,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,I think we're okay.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.46,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.34,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:15.71,0:21:18.72,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lulu-chan's so friendly!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:18.72,0:21:20.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I think we'll get along great!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.73,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.65,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.57,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Did Mari-chan like the confection?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.57,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah, she loved it.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:42.99,0:21:44.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Where's big sis?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.70,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,She's in her room.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.08,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.60,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,You won't give it to her?
