Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.64,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bae, bae, bae
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.02,0:00:41.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bubee, bubee
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae, bae
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Ooh, ooh, ooh
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}You're my little buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Hey, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bubee, bubee, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}My heart is racing like crazy{ドキドキしている私}
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.62,0:01:02.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}And right before my eyes{この目に映るのは}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Are the colors of a brand new world{新しい世界の色}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Whoa
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Stay with me today{今日もそばにいて}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.22,0:01:13.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}We'll walk hand in hand{君の手を取って行こう}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.22,0:01:17.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Dreaming of the place where we can become light{光に成れる場所に憧れて}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.60,0:01:23.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I can hear the magic{魔法の音がする}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I wanna sing with you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.52,0:01:28.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Let's sing together{二人で歌おう}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.53,0:01:32.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}You're a bright shining star{君は明るく輝く星}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}My bubee, bubee, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}We can be shining stars
