Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:38.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Alone!){「alone！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:42.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Even if the stars in a moonless sky{もしも月のない 空に星が}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:44.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Still twinkle{輝いても}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:45.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(No magic!){「no magic！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:49.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Even if the clouds in a sunless sky{もしも太陽がない 空の雲が}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:52.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Still drift{流れてても}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:54.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I feel so lonely{淋しそうに}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(I was always right beside you){『当たり前に隣に居た』}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I'm searching for you{君を探してる}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I'll frame a photo of us two and hang it up{二人映る 額縁(frame)Decorate！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:06.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Let's set things the way we want, the way we will, the way they are{思うがまま ワガまま ありのままに並べよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:10.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Take our chemistry, plus+, minus-, multiplied×, divided÷ by...{相性 Plus＋ Minus－ Multiply× Divide÷ by…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:10.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I love it every way{「全部好き」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:14.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Calling me, calling you{Calling me Calling you}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(And you){「＆you」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I want to walk up the stairs of the future with you{君と歩きたい 未来階段(stairs)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Lucky lucky shiny, our beating hearts dreamin' away{Lucky Lucky Shiny 二人の ときめきDreamin’}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:24.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}If there's clear skies tomorrow, everything will be okay{明日晴れなら 万事オーライ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:28.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Maybe I'm a bit sad and weak{ちょっとブルー Weakness}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:29.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(But I'm happy!){(but happy)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:32.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}But when I'm with you I feel safe{けど君が居るから Being saved}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:34.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}There's no such thing as wasted time{無駄な時間なんて無い}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:35.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Let's wait until the rain stops{雨上がる空をWaiting}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Check it out, look up at the sky{Check it out 見上げたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:42.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Courage is in two worlds, yeah, together now{Courage is in two worlds そう Together now}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:43.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Proof!){「proof！」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}That's what binds us together{「それが 二つ 結ぶ絆だから」}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:52.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}What kind of future will the spotlight shine on?{どんな明日を照らすのかspotlight}

